data.description:
Gorgeous, updated townhome in the Village of Cedarbend. Come and make this partially furnished unit your home or even better, your winter escape! Cedarbend is centrally located to shopping, Fort Myers Beach, Sanibel, and all that Fort Myers has to offer. The unit has 2 bedrooms upstairs, two full bathrooms, in-unit laundry, and a beautifully updated kitchen with freshly painted cabinets, new appliances (2023), and tile backsplash. There are tile floors throughout the downstairs and carpet up the stairs and in the bedrooms. There is also a community pool for those warm summer days. Don't forget your private courtyard that can easily be filled with plants and a grill to make it your own private oasis.

Renter will be responsible for electricity and internet. Renter will also be responsible for filling out a background check with the HOA. A $150 fee is required for this, as well as a $40/adult application fee. The minimum lease is 12 months. No smoking in the unit. 2 parking spots are designated for the unit.
